<object id="GUID-272C71ED-2A34-475F-941F-CE780E1682E7" class="- topic/object "><desc class="- topic/desc "><p class="- topic/p ">Execute selected printer calibrations </p></desc><param name="testid" value="216003" class="- topic/param "/><param name="target" value="NIL" class="- topic/param "/><param name="axmodule" value="None" class="- topic/param "/></object> 
</p></section><section id="GUID-2B0A8171-7154-4EA9-BB1B-748197F79CAB" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "/><fig id="GUID-360CB32F-AA9C-4F4D-8DD7-25B2F9185E14" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-7D4F930D-2F75-4110-9E51-DF8E02096C58-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-7D4F930D-2F75-4110-9E51-DF8E02096C58-low.png"/></fig></section><section id="GUID-1156E15C-FA11-42F7-80CE-F9823F371FA9" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Function</title><p class="- topic/p ">Execute the calibrations that were selected in 
<xref keyref="SDS21-6-002" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-D650BDBB-4674-4B96-BD64-98FDD9BAF4CB.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 21-6-002 Select required printer calibrations [Special Tests]?>21-6-002 Select required printer calibrations [Special Tests]</xref>. 
</p><note id="GUID-88B504FD-35C9-4BFB-913F-2C0F7D2753B1" class="- topic/note "><p class="- topic/p "> Switch winding off before you start this test (via service user mode -&gt; output -&gt; select winding mode: no). 
</p></note></section><section id="GUID-A72FF491-D6BB-46AD-8E99-5FF66AB11223" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Description</title><p class="- topic/p ">This test can be run more than once to execute the remaining calibrations in case of any previous errors. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">You need white, smooth, opaque media of at least 50 inch wide for this test. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">If the media thickness for the medium is not available or incorrect enter the correct media thickness during this test. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> Double check that the media thickness is set correctly. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "> 
<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "> For Service calibration media use SDS parameters 25-1-004 (Vinyl), 5 (Film) or 6 Paper).</b> 
</p></section><section id="GUID-FC1A5647-3DD6-4EB7-82C7-5384149C6EC4" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Procedure </title><ol class="- topic/ol "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Start the test. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Select the roll to use. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Press Continue. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Double check and confirm the media thickness 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">Press Continue. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">The calibrations are now carried out. 
</p></li><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p ">In case of errors, you can restart the test. 
</p></li></ol></section></taskbody><related-links class="- topic/related-links "><linkpool class="- topic/linkpool " mapkeyref="GUID-8A41CFEA-5928-4042-A2CB-507A5D034160"><link class="- topic/link " mapclass="- map/topicref " format="dita" type="concept" href="generated-topic-GUID-3AD12DA3-F651-4B11-BEB9-FD79AA9649BB.xml" role="parent"><?ditaot usertext?><linktext class="- topic/linktext "><?ditaot usertext?>SDS</linktext></link></linkpool></related-links>
